Fair enough on the Star Wars references. I'll make a quick edit.

As for the use of MTF Kappa-10, and MTF Gamma-13, I feel that since these two MTFs have very fundamentally different missions their inclusion is not too wacky. Gamma-13 is the MTF specifically designed to handle all things Anderson. Meanwhile, since all the members of Kappa-10 are AI's, I feel that they would be a good first choice for looking into a secure database unnoticed. There is also a precedent for them breaking into MCD computer systems.







